==German==
===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[simile]]'' "similar": from a standardized bureaucratic form in monarchistic Austria called ''simile''. Nowadays understood to mean ''Schimmel'' "white horse".
===Noun===
'''Amtsschimmel'''
# a surplus of bureaucracy, [[red tape]]
====Homophones====
*[[Schimmel]] (mold)
*[[Schimmel]] (horse)

